cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.CC

This paper discusses the use of Datalog and its extensions in databases and artificial intelligence, which are both covered by cs.DB and cs.AI respectively. The paper also focuses on knowledge representation and reasoning, which falls under cs.LO. The complexity analysis mentioned in the abstract suggests that the paper may also be relevant to cs.DS and cs.CC.
